<h2 class='page-intro'>A CES speaker is a thought leader, an innovative thinker and an industry influencer.</h2>
<p class="intro">CES 2018 Call for Speakers is open through&nbsp;<strong>July 14</strong>.<br />
<br />
<a href="/Conference/Speaker-Resources/Call-for-Speakers.aspx"><img alt="Apply to Speak" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/apply-to-speak-button_350x70.jpg" /></a></p>  

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;margin-top: -10px;">Important Dates</h3>

<p><strong>July 14:</strong>&nbsp;CES Call for Speakers closes<br />
<strong>Oct.&nbsp;12:&nbsp;</strong>Applicants notified of speaking status&nbsp;</p>

<h2><br />
About CES Call for Speakers Submissions</h2>

<p>Only one submission is allowed per speaker. This submission should contain speaking expertise and experience related to the one speaker that is submitted. Each submission may contain up to three speaking themes for this individual.</p>

<p><strong>New this year!&nbsp;</strong>There is a limit of five submissions per company, so please coordinate with colleagues within your organization prior to submitting.&nbsp;</p>

<p><u><strong>Note:</strong></u>&nbsp;You must complete the form&nbsp;in one sitting. You will not have the ability&nbsp;to download or edit your submission after it&#39;s complete. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;">Select Your Session&nbsp;Theme</h3>

<p>Each speaker may apply for up to three of&nbsp;the following themes:&nbsp;</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="width:100%;">
	<tbody>
