<br />
<strong>Speaking at C Space </strong><br />
C Space&nbsp;speaking opportunities &mdash; about content, branding, marketing and entertainment&nbsp; &mdash; &nbsp;are currently managed by invitation only. For inquiries, please contact <a href="mailto:CESconference@cta.tech">CESconference@cta.tech</a>.

<h2><br />
Tips for a Successful Submission</h2>

<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
	<li><strong>Know the CES audience.</strong>&nbsp;Our&nbsp;audience comprises qualified consumer technology industry attendees looking for real B2B applications.&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Review your form </strong>carefully before submitting.&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Do not pitch products</strong>, companies or services. Submissions contain clear takeaways for the audience.&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Link to the speaker bio</strong> on the contact information page. Make sure the speaker bio is clear on why this person is an authority on subject matter.&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Provide case studies or research</strong> that will assist the audience in their own business applications.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

